  "detailed_description": "\"Pickup Point Simulator\" is a first-person simulator in which you will encounter all the intricacies of working at a pickup location.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/b13768ccd570e5e8563e9e8b7f9ec395.avif?t=1744131756\" width=677 height=91 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/b6934b305c50864d072d5a6007e11af9.poster.avif?t=1744131756\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/b6934b305c50864d072d5a6007e11af9.webm?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/b6934b305c50864d072d5a6007e11af9.mp4?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take care of the interior design, influencing its comfort and efficiency. You will decide how your point will look like, and customers will appreciate your ideas and leave feedback. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/86bd1defead49f618797b2122c44585e.avif?t=1744131756\" width=651 height=91 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/e9cf672991216754826233e3c022fa91.poster.avif?t=1744131756\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/e9cf672991216754826233e3c022fa91.webm?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/e9cf672991216754826233e3c022fa91.mp4?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You will have to order deliveries on time and make sure that your warehouse is always full. And what categories of goods to choose - it's up to you. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/016adc86ac3581e439ea22986fc7f2b4.avif?t=1744131756\" width=652 height=91 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/98477894a7a7bdb176fcef999335299a.poster.avif?t=1744131756\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/98477894a7a7bdb176fcef999335299a.webm?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/98477894a7a7bdb176fcef999335299a.mp4?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Scan the QR-code, find the right product, give it to the customer and don't forget to make sure that your customers are satisfied.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/f02c5c7e92926f9f43c76e1a0a1ed0b5.avif?t=1744131756\" width=651 height=91 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/051490cc810ae386de4c032d1f478203.poster.avif?t=1744131756\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/051490cc810ae386de4c032d1f478203.webm?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/051490cc810ae386de4c032d1f478203.mp4?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Upgrade not only your pickup point, but also yourself: open new opportunities by acquiring skills to create the most successful business in your neighbourhood.",
